My name is Captain Badi Bassim.

34:13.458 --> 34:16.458
I'm here to start work
with, uh, General McMahon.

34:17.417 --> 34:19.750
- Who?
- McMahon.

34:19.833 --> 34:21.625
- McMahon?
- Yeah.

34:23.000 --> 34:27.083
- Why are you not wearing the uniform?
