53:17.083 --> 53:19.875
We have the gala dinner right after.
We don't have any wiggle room here.

53:19.958 --> 53:22.375
[GREG] You should wear the fatigues
to the thing this afternoon.

53:22.458 --> 53:24.875
The general, direct from the battlefield.

53:26.000 --> 53:28.542
