Uh, sir, before you get dragged
into the hubbub there,

58:42.792 --> 58:45.125
I want to introduce you
to Sean Cullen here.

58:45.208 --> 58:48.417
Sean's the writer from <i>Rolling Stone.</i>
He's been doing that profile piece on you.

58:48.500 --> 58:50.750
He's gonna be tagging along
for a couple days.

58:50.833 --> 58:53.125
Thanks for having me, sir.
It's a real privilege.

58:53.917 --> 58:55.667
<i>- Rolling Stone?</i>
- Yes, sir.

58:55.750 --> 58:56.958
Just make sure I'm on the cover.

58:58.042 --> 59:00.667
Well, it's between you and Lady Gaga, sir.

59:01.625 --> 59:05.000
Well, put me in a heart-shaped
bathtub with her.

59:05.083 --> 59:06.917
- Rose petals. Happy to share.
- [BOTH CHUCKLING]

59:07.000 --> 59:10.292
Glen, stop joking. [LAUGHING]

59:10.375 --> 59:12.667
I'm deadly serious, son.
Put me on the cover.

59:12.750 --> 59:13.875
[LAUGHS]

59:15.208 --> 59:16.208
[CLEARS THROAT]

59:22.333 --> 59:25.500
Okay, here we are.
There's the boss. There's Mrs. Boss.

59:26.333 --> 59:28.917
[GREG] Oh, there's me. There's you.

