01:08:24.542 --> 01:08:26.207
[CORY] Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!

01:08:27.207 --> 01:08:30.082
[PETE] Boss and Mrs. Boss, down there.

01:08:30.167 --> 01:08:31.417
