- I'm hungry.

01:31:25.542 --> 01:31:27.333
I wanna eat that motherfucker.

01:31:27.417 --> 01:31:29.000
[SOLDIER] Jesus Christ, man.

01:31:33.833 --> 01:31:34.875
Farrenberg.

01:31:44.917 --> 01:31:45.917
Move.

01:31:56.167 --> 01:31:58.375
- [SNIPER RIFLE FIRING]
- Contact front!

01:31:58.458 --> 01:31:59.667
[SOLDIER] Move! Move! Up against the wall!

01:31:59.750 --> 01:32:00.792
- Farrenberg.
- [SOLDIER] Not too close.

01:32:00.875 --> 01:32:02.583
Get off the walls. Now!

01:32:10.375 --> 01:32:12.500
- Fuck!
- [SOLDIER] Over there, twelve o'clock!

01:32:13.083 --> 01:32:15.292
[ORTEGA] Cole! Cole!

01:32:15.375 --> 01:32:17.958
I need to see a weapon.
