- Corporal, what's happening?
- Wait, where the fuck are you going, man?

01:35:51.333 --> 01:35:53.375
- Shut the fuck up!
- Wait, Cole! Cole!

01:35:53.458 --> 01:35:55.792
- Cole! Get back here, Cole!
- [SOLDIER 1] Cole!

01:35:55.875 --> 01:35:58.000
[SOLDIER 2] Cole, what the fuck, man?
